accTitle: Mermaid colour support
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid colour hints mapped onto sequencer colour properties.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/27-colour-support/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/27-colour-support
}
